Class DescribeBlock

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tenforce.semtech.SPARQLParser.SPARQLStatements.DescribeBlock

    IStatement

    public class DescribeBlock
extends java.lang.Object
implements IStatement
    Created by langens-jonathan on 25.07.16. version 0.0.1 Parses a correct describe SPARQL block inside a SPARQL query. It looks like DESCRIBE ?x, ?y WHERE { /WHERE CLAUSE/ }
